data.name: TextBox1.Text
data.value: Subtitle Renamer is a program to rename subtitles with their corresponding video files. You can drag a folder that contains video files and subtitles into the list to load them. You can exclude sub files from changing their names. You can also specify the added extensions while importing the folder.
